{"tid":1376914,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"建議以後只係喺機場集會","createTime":"2019-07-28T12:30:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T11:12:10.000Z","uid":127532,"like":372,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":68,"replies":[{"pid":"bc549f9d9e5aa2aac662325f3381018525c16ce6","tid":1376914,"uid":127532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T12:30:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">機場係最安全，因為佢哋唔夠膽清場<br />\n一清場，機場就會癱瘓，其他國家都要發旅遊警告<br />\n所以政府唔到最後關頭都唔敢清<br />\n佢要清場付出嘅代價都會好大</span><br />\n<br />\n但機場不宜勇武，我哋要做到係政府暴力清場，唔係示威者攪到機場癱瘓"},{"pid":"cb705811632a32281d0f01b90fb69454e1873f6b","tid":1376914,"uid":127532,"like":125,"dislike":2,"score":123,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T12:35:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abc6debce6078b8e64b7b0782c36da4bdc5df133","tid":1376914,"uid":127532,"like":48,"dislike":1,"score":47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T12:37:24.000Z","msg":"最近呢幾次示威已見疲態<br />\n我唔忍心再見到兄弟被打被拉<br />\n<br />\n贊成既請幫推"},{"pid":"deae7e140820b71c33ef80b61da885110a6e9544","tid":1376914,"uid":42064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T12:39:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3f816e23a4c6c42ab231487d66584922dbcc61ba","tid":1376914,"uid":42064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T12:39:28.000Z","msg":"認同請分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee26ec86cfdd8d83e548897a941f1b1093e5a3b7","tid":1376914,"uid":127532,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T12:41:46.000Z","msg":"尊重勇武既義士，我真係唔想再見到你地被人打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但請你地抖一抖，入機場嘆下先<br />\n依家距離開學9月1日死線仲有一個月<br />\n我地日日佔機場，兩個星期政府一定要做野"},{"pid":"a04356d8dffa3f25290fb8184b13fb0aa697cd59","tid":1376914,"uid":59633,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T12:43:11.000Z","msg":"照清架，唔可以用常理諗班狗"},{"pid":"26575024e315bc03967e155c16340e085b08f43a","tid":1376914,"uid":127532,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T12:44:21.000Z","msg":"機場另一個好處係多外國遊客<br />\n呢單野一定要外國幫拖先有機會贏<br />\n要靠外國俾經濟壓力香港同大陸"},{"pid":"58720f6b3a1366d2ec409b99d0a68a93ad34bde4","tid":1376914,"uid":290385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T12:44:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ee4c78ccbd84dd880ac424fce53be2d47d8e2a4a","tid":1376914,"uid":127532,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"a04356d8dffa3f25290fb8184b13fb0aa697cd59","tid":1376914,"uid":59633,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T12:43:11.000Z","msg":"照清架，唔可以用常理諗班狗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T12:46:45.000Z","msg":"我知佢最後一定要清，但政府要付出既大價大好多<br />\n機場係唯一一區政府損失大過示威者既區<br />\n呢兩日大家見到，每一次我地都會損失幾個走得最前既兄弟，而<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>政府係無損失</strong></span><br />\n唔化算"},{"pid":"8b1f12ae8f321dabf8dcd41a476e521b032533a0","tid":1376914,"uid":263186,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T12:48:22.000Z","msg":"金鐘、機場、元朗 無限loop"},{"pid":"9c7f7f7b8ebf146f0b5b332a7db352bc91778a53","tid":1376914,"uid":127532,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"8b1f12ae8f321dabf8dcd41a476e521b032533a0","tid":1376914,"uid":263186,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T12:48:22.000Z","msg":"金鐘、機場、元朗 無限loop"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T12:50:02.000Z","msg":"我認為其他地區成本太高<br />\n依家拉一個少一個<br />\n同埋警方愈來愈暴力，和理非已經唔太敢出去"},{"pid":"add6c1fa7db4a7eb238df08e04f2847d2bffba44","tid":1376914,"uid":175673,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T12:51:34.000Z","msg":"支持機場，運動要有noise先有用。"},{"pid":"c76bc364ffe93dfe9cbe89a550f25969c28e3b99","tid":1376914,"uid":127532,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T12:53:49.000Z","msg":"機場一樣會有俾人拉既風險<br />\n估計警方會係各個地鐵站抄牌<br />\n建議我地將所有物資留係機場，包括裝備、黑衫，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">一身清白咁返市區</span></strong><br />\n單程飛出入<br />\n遇到抄牌唔駛同佢講係機場出黎"},{"pid":"1f8e7aaca1ade5cb12dd3dcc7ac3feaa6275a8c3","tid":1376914,"uid":78241,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T12:54:04.000Z","msg":"玩輸出同宣傳，好似西九膠鐵咁<br />\n<br />\n明明之前西九個效果幾好，好多手足都認同，係唔知點解無咗件事。"},{"pid":"f8e040fec9e3983a1e150afae542f1c524de9f7f","tid":1376914,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T12:54:37.000Z","msg":"旅遊區都重work嘅"},{"pid":"0d4add986610c96011f16a5ea7971831cd1838e3","tid":1376914,"uid":127532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T12:54:51.000Z","msg":"我建議24小時佔領"},{"pid":"9ce7f13ececa5b4221d2bf0b6c5f12b99ea4de48","tid":1376914,"uid":216710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T12:57:30.000Z","msg":"支持發起下次機場行動"},{"pid":"93fb96331a93f47faf0316d95a7c9c94feeee67e","tid":1376914,"uid":278053,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T12:58:03.000Z","msg":"建議8月1號起，無限期馬拉松式接機，有冇得諗？？<br />\n俾返少少時間文宣做野同動員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eba33be28aa4ab9c5662596d42bf1fa38e590105","tid":1376914,"uid":127532,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"f8e040fec9e3983a1e150afae542f1c524de9f7f","tid":1376914,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T12:54:37.000Z","msg":"旅遊區都重work嘅"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T13:01:02.000Z","msg":"依家佢一律唔發不反對通知書，其實為左令遊行唔合法<br />\n同埋俾到理由佢亂放催淚彈<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">政府打算令到和理非遊行既空間愈來愈少</span></strong><br />\n我認為要變陣"},{"pid":"0437b0f2b30b77febc20043f25f554f5e68aff50","tid":1376914,"uid":127532,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"93fb96331a93f47faf0316d95a7c9c94feeee67e","tid":1376914,"uid":278053,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T12:58:03.000Z","msg":"建議8月1號起，無限期馬拉松式接機，有冇得諗？？<br />\n俾返少少時間文宣做野同動員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T13:01:27.000Z","msg":"支持！最緊要齊心"},{"pid":"ab4803660b1d6971b09ce9ba2a4371f5c72b99